extensionDescription.message: LinkedIn Container omoha’eño ne rembiapo LinkedIn pegua ambue mba’e ñandutípe rejapóvagui, omboyke hag̃ua LinkedIn ohapykuehóvo okápe oikóva  iñanduti rendágui kookie mbohapyháva rupive.
extensionDescription.description: Description of the extension. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

in-fbc-p1.message: LinkedIn ikatu ohapykueho ko tenda ko’ag̃aite. Embogueséramo LinkedIn oguerekohágui, eiporavo “Tenda LinkedIn guerekoha moneĩmbyre” ha emboguete tysýigui.

on-facebook-subhead.message: LinkedIn ha tenda oĩ LinkedIn Container mboypýri gotyo
on-facebook-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

on-facebook-p1.message: Ko ta’ãngachu’i ejuhúta Firefox kundaharape rendápe eikévo tenda LinkedIn.com mba’épe térã embojuajúramo LinkedIn Container rehe.
on-facebook-p1.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened into LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

on-facebook-p2.message: Oiko porã hag̃ua, ko’ã tenda oikotevẽ oike heratee LinkedIn pegua ndive, he’iséva avei LinkedIn ikatuha nde rapykueho ejapóva guivépe.
on-facebook-p2.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop up when the user is on LinkedIn.

notOnLinkedInHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

notOnLinkedInText.message: Ko tenda ndaipóri LinkedIn Container ryepýpe. Upéicha rupi asyve LinkedIn ohapykuehóvo ñandutípe.
notOnLinkedInText.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a LinkedIn website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE LinkedIn Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

onUnknownSiteHeader.message: Ko tenda ndaipóri LinkedIn Container ryepýpe.
onUnknownSiteHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on an "unknown" website - e.g., about:newtab. DO NOT TRANSLATE "LinkedIn Container".

facebookContainer.description: This is the name of the extension, and appears at the top of all onboarding panels. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container".

onboarding1-subhead.description: This is the subhead of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding1-p1.message: LinkedIn ikatu nde rapykueho LinkedIn.com-gui esẽ rire. Techapyrã, umi votõ “Ahayhu” ha “Moherakuã” ikatu ohapykueho moõpa eikéra’e, umi kuatiarogue ehayhu’ỹva ha neremoherakuãiva’ekue.
onboarding1-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding1-p2.message: LinkedIn Container omoheñói opaha tendakuéra LinkedIn ha ambue ñandutigua, péicha LinkedIn-pe hasyve nderapykueho hag̃ua eikundahahápe.

onboarding2-subhead.message: LinkedIn ha tenda oĩ LinkedIn Container mboypýri
onboarding2-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding2-alt.description: This is alternative text for the icon in the second onboarding panel

onboarding2-p1.message: Ko ta’ãngachu’i ejuhúta Firefox kundaharape rendápe eikévo tenda LinkedIn.com-pe, oĩva LinkedIn Container mboypýri gotyo.
onboarding2-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the second onboarding panel.

onboarding2-p2.message: Oiko porã hag̃ua, ko’ã tenda oikotevẽ oike heratee LinkedIn pegua ndive, he’iséva avei LinkedIn ikatu nde rapykueho ejapóva guivépe.
onboarding2-p2.description: This is the second paragraph of the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "LinkedIn Container"

onboarding4-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-p1.message: Ndereikéirõ jepe LinkedIn-pe, kóva nde rapykuehokuaa ñandutípe. Umi votõ omoneĩva ehupi hag̃ua LinkedIn-pe térã emoñepyrũvo tembiapo ñanduti rendápe eiporúvo mba’ete LinkedIn pegua oreko tapykuehoha. LinkedIn Container ojoko ko’ã tapykuehoha ha ohechauka ta’ãnga’i ehecha hag̃ua moõpa oñemboguekuaa.
onboarding4-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-img.message: Ko ta’ãnga ohechauka mba’éichapa ehecháta LinkedIn Containers ra’ãnga’i kuatiaroguépe votõ Ahayhu LinkedIn pegua ykére.
onboarding4-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-subhead.message: Eñepyrũ tembiapo LinkedIn ndive ambue tendápe
onboarding5-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p1.message: Eiporu hag̃ua ne rembiapo ñepyrũ LinkedIn-pe ambue tendápe, emongu’ekuaa ikatuha peve. Eikutu pe ta’ãnga’i ha eiporavo ‘Emoneĩ tenda LinkedIn Container-pe’ iguypeve gotyo.
onboarding5-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-img.message: Ko ta’ãnga ohechauka mba’éichapa ojehecháta pe votõ embojuaju hag̃ua tenda LinkedIn Container rehe ta’ãngarupápe.
onboarding5-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p2.message: Kóva omoneĩ oñepyrũvo tembiapo LinkedIn ndive, avei omoneĩ LinkedIn-pe ohapykuehóvo ne rembiapo.
onboarding5-p2.description: This is the second paragraph on the fifth onboarding panel.

btn-allow.description: This is a button to allows users to whitelist the domain, adding it to the LinkedIn container.

btn-cancel.description: This is a button to cancel out of the onboarding panel.

btn-next.description: This is a button to continue to the next onboarding panel.

btn-back.description: This is a button that returns the user to the previous onboarding panel.

btn-done.description: This is a button the user clicks to close out the panel when they have finished reading the text.

btn-arrow-back.description: This is alternative text for the back arrow button.

btn-arrow-forward.description: This is alternative text for the arrow icon next to the "How LinkedIn Container Works" link

no-trackers-p1.message: LinkedIn Container ndohechái LinkedIn rapykuehoha ko kuatiaroguépe. Peicharamojepe, ko kuatiarogue ikatu oreko ambue jehapykuehoha.

learn-more.description: This is a link that opens a page with more information about LinkedIn Container.

how-fbc-works.description: This is a button that opens the LinkedIn Container onboarding flow.

trackers-detected-subhead.description: This is a subhead, and it means that the add on has protected the user by blocking LinkedIn trackers.

trackers-detected-p1.message: Umi votõ LinkedIn pegua ojehecháva kuatiarogue jejoguaha, marandu, ha ambue, oreko tapykuehoha omombe’úva LinkedIn-pe umi kuatiarogue eike hague. Ndereiporúiramo jepe ko’ã votõ, umi tapykuehoha ikatu ombyaty marandu ne ñeikundaha rehegua. LinkedIn Container ojoko umi tapykuehoha.

trackers-detected-p2.message: LinkedIn Container ojoko ko’ã jehapykuehoha. Hákatu eikutúramo oimeraẽva votõ, LinkedIn ikatukuaa ohapykueho.

trackers-detected-fence-alt.description: This is alternative text describing the container fence icon.

sites-included.description: This is a header for the list of websites that are in the LinkedIn Container by default. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the language.

no-sites-added.description: This message is shown beneath the 'SITES YOU’VE ALLOWED' list header when no sites have been added to the contaner.

sites-allowed.description: This is the header for the list of sites the user has manually added into the LinkedIn Container. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the lanaguage.

sites-added-p1.message: LinkedIn Container omohenda LinkedIn mba’etee kora ryepýpe. Ikatu omoneĩ ambue tenda kora ryepýpe, hákatu kóva omoneĩta LinkedIn-pe ohapykuehovévo ne ñeikundaha ñandutípe.

button-allow-site.description: Button text that allows sites to be added to the LinkedIn Container

button-remove-site.description: Button text that removes an already-added site from the LinkedIn Container to the default container

button-remove-site-tooltip.message: Ko tenda ha’e rupi LinkedIn mba’e, ndaikatumo’ãi oñembogue LinkedIn Container-gui.
button-remove-site-tooltip.description: Tooltip that is displayed when hovering over the remove site button

remove-site-p1.message: Emboguévo ko tenda LinkedIn Container-gui Tembiapo Ñepyrũ rembiapoite LinkedIn pegua ndoikomo’ãvéima ha umi kookie tapykuehoha LinkedIn rehegua oguepáta.

remove-site-p2.message: Emoñepyrũjey hag̃ua tembiapo LinkedIn ndive ipyahúva, eikotevẽta embojuajujey LinkedIn Container rehe.

add-site-p1.message: Kóva omoneĩta emoñepyrũvo tembiapo LinkedIn ndive, omoneĩta LinkedIn-pe ohapykuehóvo ne rembiapo ko tendápe.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share.message: LinkedIn Container oipe’a ko votõ ha ojoko og̃uahẽva jehapykueho ko kuatiarogue pegua LinkedIn guive.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-login.message: LinkedIn Container ojokóma ijehapykuehoha. Eiporúramo tembiapo ñepyrũ LinkedIn ndive ko tendápe, ikatu nde rapykueho.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p2.message: Eiporúramo tembiapo ñepyrũ LinkedIn ndive, LinkedIn ikatu ohapykueho ne rembiapo ko tendápe. Kóva ikatu ne pytyvõ ehechauka hag̃ua nde rekove porãha eikundahávo ñandutípe.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share-passive.message: Eikutúvo ko votõ, LinkedIn ikatukuaa ohapykueho nde jeike ko tendápe.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-email.message: Eiporúramo ne ñanduti vevete ko’ápe, ikatu LinkedIn ohapykueho ndehegui. Eikutu eikuaasevéramo.

inPageUI-tooltip-email-prompt-p2.message: Ko tenda omoherakuãkuaa ñanduti veve kundaharape LinkedIn ndive, omoneĩva LinkedIn-pe nde rapykuehóvo. Eiporu Firefox Relay eñomi hag̃ua ne ñanduti veve.
